CustomField.description: This field is conditionally required and must be specified if the LLC_BI__Post_to_Parent_Object_2__c field is set to TRUE. It is manually populated. The field indicates the object type that contains the field (specified by LLC_BI__Field_Name_2__c) that will be updated with the value of the calculated statistic when the LLC_BI__Post_to_Parent_Object_2__c field is set to TRUE.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Name of the object proceeding where additional output will be placed.
CustomField.label: Object Name 2
